[thinking] **Exploring proxy generation issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering whether proxy generation is throwing a RuntimeException that wraps an InaccessibleObjectException instead of an Error on the JVM. If I test externally with JDK21, perhaps Graal TCK may allow some modules to open. However, if that doesn't work, the test will fail. The existing Javassist Loader uses defineClass and possibly only catches Errors. I might also look into whether Gradle adds --add-opens. Time to search for more!
